799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adverts featuring the US supermodel for a relaunch of an Adidas shoe from the1972 Munich Olympics were pulledon Friday, after pro-Israel groups called them \\\"sick\\\" and offensive.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996956138756707, \"rank\": 0.0001494214366905256, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid - whose father is Palestinian - has been outspoken againstIsrael'swar on Hamas.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1050762566187322e-16, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After reports suggested Hadid was considering legal action against Adidas, the company has now issued an apology to the model, and a number of others.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8951735893207918e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Connections continue to be made to the terrible tragedy that occurred at the Munich Olympics due to our recent SL72 campaign,\\\" it said on its Adidas Originals Instagram feed.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.705953675942606e-12, \"text\": \"Adidas Originals\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7212259547059375e-12, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These connections are not meant, and we apologise for any upset or distress caused to communities around the world.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We made an unintentional mistake.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also apologise to our partners,Bella Hadid, ASAP Nast, Jules Kound\\u00e9, and others, for any negative impact on them and we are revising the campaign.\\\"\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ASAP Nast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999990449064184, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jules Kound\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bella Hadid responds to Adidas shoe campaign controversy  Supermodel Bella Hadid's Adidas campaign pulled after being called 'sick'  Supermodel Bella Hadid cl